1
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:27,120
Put me down. I can manage on my own.

2
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:30,280
Your foot hasn't healed yet. Don't push yourself.

3
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:33,840
Thank you for tonight.

4
00:00:35,480 --> 00:00:36,760
Remember to apply the ointment when you get back.

5
00:00:36,760 --> 00:00:38,880
Rest up for the next few days.

6
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:40,520
Okay.

7
00:00:41,160 --> 00:00:42,720
What about your family?

8
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:46,240
I'll go back when my dad sorts things out.

9
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:47,880
Okay.

10
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:50,320
We're here.

11
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:04,620
I'm heading in.

12
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,200
Yin Zixi.

13
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,960
Yes?

14
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:23,720
I like you.

15
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,920
What did you say?

16
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,360
Nothing.

17
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:31,130
Be careful going upstairs.

18
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,440
Okay.

19
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,400
Do you know who ordered this?

20
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,160
I don't know.

21
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,720
I just heard someone wants to make trouble for Yin Zixi,

22
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:47,360
but they didn't contact anyone inside the student council.

23
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:49,160
Let me know if you find any clues.

24
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,120
Okay.

25
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:14,360
What exactly did he want to say then?

26
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:19,440
I accidentally sprained my ankle during the photoshoot today.

27
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:22,000
Thankfully An Yufan was there.

28
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:25,520
I hope I didn't take up too much of his time.

29
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,240
Xixi,

30
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,400
did you read the tips I gave you?

31
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,920
I finished it.

32
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,920
Then why haven't I seen you stream?

33
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,600
I'm still preparing.

34
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,160
Still preparing?

35
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:39,020
You can't miss this opportunity.

36
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:41,920
Mom, I don't even have a place to stream.

37
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:43,760
Can't you just do it in your dorm?

38
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,079
No.

39
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:47,560
Streaming at school isn't that simple.

40
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,120
Xixi,

41
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:51,360
isn't Yin Zixi doing a great job?

42
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,600
Don't waste my efforts, okay?

43
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,840
I'm not like her.

44
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,600
She has a sugar daddy pushing her up the ranks,

45
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,560
and a senior giving her backstage support.

46
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,420
How can I do it when I have nothing?

47
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,360
You build it up as you go.

48
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,440
How will you know if it works if you don't try?

49
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,920
Maybe resources will come as you stream.

50
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:09,160
I will help you too,

51
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,600
sweetie.

52
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:13,160
I also found a batch of new designer clothes.

53
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,320
If you stream with these clothes...

54
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,440
As a style reflecting the form of news,

55
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,160
Wow.

56
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,120
Look at this.

57
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:25,400
it mainly includes news, communications, news features, and exclusive interviews.

58
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:28,330
News is presented in the most direct and concise way.

59
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,040
Who did this?

60
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,280
Is it true?

61
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,840
There are even photos.

62
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,760
I didn't expect her to be like this.

63
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:36,480
Well, she is an internet celebrity.

64
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,280
What's wrong?

65
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:00,840
What is this?

66
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,600
What do you want?

67
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:06,320
This is the card I found at the scene where Yin Zixi was kidnapped.

68
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,440
Did you arrange it?

69
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:12,080
What does an internet cafe have to do with me?

70
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,320
Stop playing dumb.

71
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,520
The off-campus esports competitions every year,

72
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:16,380
aren't they all organized by you?

73
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,080
Even if it does,

74
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,640
what can a business card prove?

75
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:29,320
If you dare touch Yin Zixi,

76
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,920
don't blame me for not being polite.

77
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:42,080
Let's begin.

78
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,200
Yes, President.

79
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,040
I understand.

80
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,800
Do it.

81
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:51,880
What are you doing?

82
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,010
Those are my things.

83
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:54,600
We received a complaint

84
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,240
saying you're doing illegal live streaming here.

85
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,240
The student union has demanded an investigation into you.

86
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,440
That's a rumor.

87
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:02,680
Can you judge right and wrong based on just one picture?

88
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,880
I don't care about that.

89
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:06,880
You are now required to stop the startup project here.

90
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:07,680
Continue.

91
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,880
Stop! Let go of my stuff!

92
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,440
Qianqian.

93
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:19,920
Isn't Yin Zixi doing well?

94
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:25,680
Don't waste Mom's good intentions, okay?

95
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,880
What are you doing?

96
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:36,090
I might have to live stream in the dorm from now on.

97
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,360
Then your dorm is fine, isn't it?

98
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,720
No.

99
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:46,700
Yin Zixi, the equipment can't be moved back to the dorm.

100
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,080
Why?

101
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:50,280
There won't be enough space in the dorm.

102
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:51,760
No, there will be.

103
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,280
Don't you have a live streaming room?

104
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,520
Why do you have to expand your business

105
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:55,640
to the dorm?

106
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:59,120
The student union won't let me use the previous venue anymore.

107
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,720
The dorm is already so small.

108
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,480
And you want to pile up so many things.

109
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:04,080
Don't you have top donators?

110
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,000
Why don't you ask them

111
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,480
to rent a bigger venue for you?

112
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,400
Yang Qian.

113
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:10,460
I really didn't expect you to see me this way too.

114
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,040
Hello.

115
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,440
Where are you?

116
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:45,280
Here.

117
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,290
What happened here?

118
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:54,080
The venue was taken back.

119
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,480
Can we move these

120
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,440
back to your apartment first?

121
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:12,730
I moved those clothes to the storage downstairs.

122
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,400
Was it the Student Union?

123
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,080
How about this.

124
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,800
Let's pause the live stream for now.

125
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,860
It's a good time for you to take a rest.

126
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,760
I'll go back and explain it clearly to the teacher

127
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:26,620
and see how to handle this matter.

128
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:29,980
I'm going to the restroom.

129
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,080
Yin Zixi.

130
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,040
I'll leave the towel on the cabinet.

131
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:53,300
I'm going out for a bit.

132
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,120
Assistant Casting Director Xi Chongjing

133
00:09:58,120 --> 00:10:00,000
Props Assistant Li Kunxiao

134
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,960
Production Vehicle Yi Mingle

135
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,840
Yitong
